org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.api.crafting

Class UnknownCraftingRecipeException

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • org.cyclops.integratedcrafting.api.crafting.UnknownCraftingRecipeException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class UnknownCraftingRecipeException
extends java.lang.Exception
    An exception for when a crafting recipe for the given instance is unavailable. The missing child recipes will only be non-null iff the collectMissingRecipes flag was enabled when calculating crafting jobs.
    See Also:
